this curiosity shapes the way we live, interact, and make

4
00:00:16,904 --> 00:00:18,826
decisions

5
00:00:18,826 --> 00:00:22,669
One of the first things people want to know is

6
00:00:22,669 --> 00:00:26,728
how to live better and improve their quality of life

7
00:00:26,728 --> 00:00:33,265
