11
00:00:47,864 --> 00:00:52,399
Humans are social creatures, and we want to know how

12
00:00:52,399 --> 00:00:55,860
others think, feel, and behave

13
00:00:55,860 --> 00:01:02,223
We want to understand social norms, culture, traditions, and values,

14
00:01:02,223 --> 00:01:06,603
because these influence how we relate to one another and

15
00:01:06,603 --> 00:01:09,837
how we fit into the larger community

16
00:01:09,837 --> 00:01:15,420
Many individuals are also interested in current events and developments

17
00:01:15,420 --> 00:01:17,350
in society

18
00:01:17,350 --> 00:01:21,640
They want to know what is happening in politics, the

19
