accidents, and disasters

24
00:01:44,763 --> 00:01:49,778
Furthermore, people are curious about justice and fairness

25
00:01:49,778 --> 00:01:54,217
They want to know how laws are applied, whether rights

26
00:01:54,217 --> 00:01:59,329
are respected, and how social inequalities can be addressed

27
00:01:59,329 --> 00:02:04,630
In addition to practical concerns, many people are driven by

28
00:02:04,630 --> 00:02:07,447
intellectual curiosity

29
00:02:07,447 --> 00:02:13,009
They want to know about history, philosophy, science, and human

30
00:02:13,009 --> 00:02:18,113
