31
00:02:18,113 --> 00:02:20,827
and how it can be improved

32
00:02:20,827 --> 00:02:25,884
Social relationships and networks are another area of interest

33
00:02:25,884 --> 00:02:30,096
People want to know who they can trust, who can

34
00:02:30,096 --> 00:02:34,249
