44
00:03:19,176 --> 00:03:23,818
In conclusion, what we want to know in society is

45
00:03:23,818 --> 00:03:30,301
diverse and multi-layered, ranging from personal well-being to understanding others,

46
00:03:30,301 --> 00:03:37,098
staying informed, ensuring safety, and contributing positively to the community

47
00:03:37,098 --> 00:03:43,204
By continuously seeking knowledge, individuals not only improve their own

48
00:03:43,204 --> 00:03:48,623
lives but also help society grow, develop, and adapt to

49
00:03:48,623 --> 00:03:50,962
the changing world

50
00:03:50,962 --> 00:03:56,061
Curiosity and the pursuit of knowledge are fundamental traits that

51
